532dc1ba8de6ed7f62486834f940ded6ea7e1","tid":196150,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T06:42:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fe878699a4aaf4cd865ad780cabf4f28c139727","tid":196150,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:42:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"487c9eb49b49b3c28af371c7348e71eb9a532ac8","tid":196150,"uid":48533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:45:57.000Z","msg":"我試過中二交野比個中文老師<br />\n中五個年班長係簿架搵返比我<br />\n原封不動冇改過"},{"pid":"55af3b392e683ada0a6285c5e77dd402b0756914","tid":196150,"uid":80598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"中四五遇到個好好既中文Miss<br />\n上堂好有心講，不過全班都冇心聽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好多時問問題都望去我同我frd嗰邊，因為得我地會答<br />\n好記得有次我拗作文有隻字我冇寫錯到，首先佢冇擺起個老師款一嚟就屌鳩我先，而係拎本字典出嚟查（當住我面），然後發現我真係冇錯，佢講咗聲Sorry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過中文考得好唔好都同Miss關係不太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d2de1a4b00d22957cd0b12ee56050874870fd8","tid":196150,"uid":6352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:52:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文科啲老師其實有無能力唔查字典下讀啱曬同解曬成本詩經/史記入面啲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中文系教授都未必得，因為字詞往往有疑義。同埋如果你只係想識難字，建議你查字典，唔需要老師。"},{"pid":"ecd02e6ce2a7c0a6e74847e5b7286801a843a216","tid":196150,"uid":14758,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T12:53:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我試過中二交野比個中文老師<br />\n中五個年班長係簿架搵返比我<br />\n原封不動冇改過</blockquote><br />\n你中五都未追過佢就姐係幫你改都冇意思啦"},{"pid":"b44c0ee6d262add3d760e0fdd6db091b6f688db6","tid":196150,"uid":72902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:02:29.000Z","msg":"中4,5中文係中文科主任教我地班<br />\n真係好有文人氣質,好多野都識,一出口講野就聽得出係讀書人,又好玩得<br />\n<br />\n最衰係教親課本內容都差唔多全班男仔訓哂<br />\n但講其他野時反而全班都好有興趣聽<br />\n<br />\n唔知係佢講書一般定係當年本教科書差:<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b12daeaef9d0e2eccd5145df204bc12dceaad235","tid":196150,"uid":34410,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:05:50.000Z","msg":"當年預科教中文個八婆淨係中意講八婆野 同埋圍爐 又奶共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e9cdbddd40079edd8b58e678aac8c2b37b3d96d","tid":196150,"uid":86378,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:07:50.000Z","msg":"垃圾中文老師：陳奕珊<br />\n有冇人相認？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43d0ffc669aff5f88f20bd6e3f4fc80ace09a2d4","tid":196150,"uid":78671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:11:02.000Z","msg":"林溢欣好似都做唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c18530a659e3725da6ec4412bb72256cc50a836e","tid":196150,"uid":550,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:15:05.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv8eZfGTcF6k&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b01e70a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k</a><br />\n根本都係侃侃而談<br />\n冇認真答過題目<br />\n當年第九味個個都答錯哂<br />\n而家都唔撚答"},{"pid":"82eb71e4b4f942c780aefcdd1bf955d782a52d74","tid":196150,"uid":80598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T13:55:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv8eZfGTcF6k&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b01e70a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k</a><br />\n根本都係侃侃而談<br />\n冇認真答過題目<br />\n當年第九味個個都答錯哂<br />\n而家都唔撚答</blockquote><br />\n第九味係邊年？"},{"pid":"bed04ce3a1cbf980af6878e15ba1001912b2b080","tid":196150,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:03:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中文科啲老師其實有無能力唔查字典下讀啱曬同解曬成本詩經/史記入面啲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中文系教授都未必得，因為字詞往往有疑義。同埋如果你只係想識難字，建議你查字典，唔需要老師。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先秦經典既話專任訓詁既prof一定得，其他朝代古文應該普通prof都得。呢個世界唔係乜都靠查，漢人點解讀先秦文章？宋元明清點解又重新再解一次？你睇既注釋，翻譯，字典都係古人訓詁出黎"},{"pid":"8c2830a45136bbfa1caa3b04788cab3b5c51853b","tid":196150,"uid":5375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:03:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中文科啲老師其實有無能力唔查字典下讀啱曬同解曬成本詩經/史記入面啲字</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n中文系教授都未必得，因為字詞往往有疑義。同埋如果你只係想識難字，建議你查字典，唔需要老師。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n先秦經典既話專任訓詁既prof一定得，其他朝代古文應該普通prof都得。呢個世界唔係乜都靠查，漢人點解讀先秦文章？宋元明清點解又重新再解一次？你睇既注釋，翻譯，字典都係古人訓詁出黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n利申中文系grad..乞緊食"},{"pid":"0716d8254c24a3e683fb7747cfdbc8f2d0187435","tid":196150,"uid":84588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:11:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><a href=\"https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fv8eZfGTcF6k&d=oVNa%2F3rGcR5VJv77DJ2le26kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=b01e70a4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/v8eZfGTcF6k</a><br />\n根本都係侃侃而談<br />\n冇認真答過題目<br />\n當年第九味個個都答錯哂<br />\n而家都唔撚答</blockquote><br />\n第九味係邊年？</blockquote><br />\n2014"},{"pid":"af37b418c29609f7522ccab5d54a2868d5bdf0a5","tid":196150,"uid":838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T14:12:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1AKYw13.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1AKYw13.jpg&h=67e3b785&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79fc6662b4d2850aad6ff61e0295368d6dca08f8","tid":196150,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-12T19:34:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets